# Quester Studio

Monorepo for **Quester** (local-first visual API flows). Use **Bun 1.3.14**.

## Packages

- `@quester/schema` — Zod validation only
- `@quester/nodes` — node `execute()` plugins
- `@quester/engine` — workspace load + flow execution
- `@quester/cli` — `quester validate` / `quester run`

Do not put execution logic in schema or UI in engine.

## Code style

- ESM with `.js` import suffixes in TypeScript
- Biome for lint/format (`bun run lint`)
- `bun:test` for tests in `src/**/*.test.ts` — add tests with every feature
- Minimal diffs; reuse existing patterns

## Flow files

- `*.flow.json` version `v1`, git-friendly workspace under `quester.json`
- Templates: `{{env.*}}`, `{{input.*}}`, `{{nodes.id}}`, `{{vars.*}}`
- Rebuild `@quester/schema` after schema changes (updates `schemas/`)

## Governance

- [CONTRIBUTING.md](../../CONTRIBUTING.md) — branches, commits, PRs
